      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been a total dream. It's in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's the perfect fit if you're looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great and feels smooth on the road. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to a good home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
