    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65B40 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to produce visceral power up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, the powertrain sends torque through a GKN ViscoLok limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically sorted, with critical preventative maintenance addressed, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis retains its factory-spec Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and aluminum multi-link suspension, ensuring sharp turn-in and mid-corner stability. The carbon fiber roof remains structurally sound, lowering the center of gravity for optimized roll gradients. While displaying minor aesthetic wear indicative of a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain within tight tolerances. A visceral, analog machine ready for the apex.",
      "price": 36500.0,
